        default void beforeSpringLoad​(BeforeSpringLoadSupplierExtensionContext context)
                       throws java.lang.Exception

        Invoked before Spring is loaded.

        This allows initial setup to be undertaken. It also allows capturing information on the current Thread as Spring loads.

        Parameters:
